dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents addresses for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2019.[This data set was developed initially automated by the WI Department of Natural Resources. It is updated and on an on-going basis, by Waushara County. The data contained in this file only covers points address information managed by the County.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The site address is a point feature class that locates situs or address locations. To provide a point for all address locations in the County. This may include multiple addresses at one point.]
